Class KuwetexServer

  • java.lang.Object

        eyes - - eyes color of the cat.
        weight - - current cat weight (kg).

      • clearLitterBox

        public static void clearLitterBox(boolean forcedClean)
                           throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Clears the litter box. Waits if cat is inside. It can be triggered for the user or by the cleaning monitor thread. Method is thread safe.
        Parameters:
        forcedClean - - true = cleaning forced by user, false = triggered by cleaning thread.
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException
